00:15:51.530 --> 00:15:58.380
In Android, especially in Honeycomb and above,
you can use RenderScript or you can use the

00:15:58.380 --> 00:16:00.990
GPU to accelerate this sort of thing.

00:16:00.990 --> 00:16:05.230
